StartInitialize ESP32
Initialize MQ-2 Sensor
Initialize DHT11 Sensor
Initialize RGB LED
Initialize Buzzer
Initialize Bluetooth
Loop Forever
Read MQ-2 Gas Value
Read Temperature
Read Humidity

If Gas Value < Safe Threshold
    Turn ON Green LED
    Turn OFF Yellow & Red LED
    Buzzer OFF
   Severity = SAFE
Else If Gas Value < Danger Threshold
    Turn ON Yellow LED
    Turn OFF Green & Red LED
    Play Medium Beep
    Severity = MODERATE
Else
    Turn ON Red LED
    Turn OFF Green & Yellow LED
    Play Long Beep
    Severity = DANGER
End If
Print Timestamp
Print Gas Value
Print Temperature
Print Humidity
Print Severity
If Severity is MODERATE or DANGER
    Send Bluetooth Alert

End I
Wait 2 Seconds
Repeat
